==Documentation==
This template creates a game rating page layout.
Uses Semantic MediaWiki for structured data storage and display.

Game Ratings are specific age/content ratings issued by rating boards (e.g., M - Mature, E - Everyone, T - Teen).

===Parameters===
{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Parameter !! Description
|-
|| Name || Display name of the rating (e.g., "M - Mature")
|-
|| Guid || Giant Bomb API identifier
|-
|| RatingBoard || The rating board that issues this rating (e.g., ESRB)
|-
|| Image || Rating image/badge
|-
|| Deck || Short description
|}

===Usage===
<pre>
{{GameRating
| Name = M - Mature
| Guid = 3065-5
| RatingBoard = RatingBoards/ESRB
| Deck = Content suitable for ages 17 and up...
}}

== Overview ==
Your wiki content here...

{{GameRatingEnd}}
</pre>
